==============================================================================
Frankl-Numerical-Coincidence-Sharpening  mg-3978
==============================================================================
Per mg-e466: 'Frankl truth iff LIFT-4-prod sgn vanishes for CE-shape F-star'
holds 100% at n=3 (12/12) and 86% at n=4 (498/582).  This probe sharpens
the 14% non-vanish at n=4 (84 families) and tests at n=5.


